dct_title_s: Homeowners and businesses on the western side of the Passaic River
dct_description_sm: Map lists homeowners & businesses on the western side of the Passaic River in Essex County.
At the westernmost point is South Canal Street, the northernmost point is Middlesex St. & Front St., easternmost is Fourth St. & southernmost is Market St.
